<ab><expan>Gnedig<ex>er</ex></expan>
<add><expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan></add>, als ir uns
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> habt von
                                <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>ochse<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan>, die Hansen Swinden
                            <expan>genome<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>word<ex>e</ex>n</expan> sind, <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> brief wol
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nome<ex>n</ex></expan> und
                            <expan>lass<ex>en</ex></expan> ewr gnad <expan>wisse<ex>n</ex></expan>,
                        daz uns das <expan>getrewl<ex>ich</ex></expan> leid ist. Und
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> auch vormals dar
                            <expan>ynne<ex>n</ex></expan> getan und das den
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>, die an <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>lantfr<ex>id</ex></expan> siczen, bevolhen, so wir peste
                                <expan>mocht<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, und <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        auch noch <expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan> unser pestes dar czü tün. Wan wo wir
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>e</ex>n</expan> lieb und dienste
                            <expan>beweise<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>möht<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, des <expan>w<ex>er</ex>n</expan> wir willig
                        und <expan>tet<ex>e</ex>n</expan> das <expan>allcz<ex>eit</ex></expan>
<expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan>. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> iiii <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan>
<expan>p<ex>ur</ex>ificac<ex>ionem</ex></expan> Marie. </ab>
